ht:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">二、时间、地点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">时间：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日（星期五<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>―<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span>）</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">地点：吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span lang=\"EN-US\">3223</span>号，人社大厦一楼）</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">三、有关要求</span></b><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、本次招聘会预设展位<span lang=\"EN-US\">64</span>个，用人单位免费进场，高校毕业生及市内相关求职者均可免费进场应聘求职。</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位请根据需要制定招聘计划。</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、请参加招聘的用人单位持营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版到吴江区人力资源市场（长安路<span lang=\"EN-US\">3223</span>号人社大厦一楼）报名或将营业执照副本、经办人身份证复印件及招聘信息电子版传真邮箱。</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">、请用人单位自行制作易拉宝、<span lang=\"EN-US\">X</span>展架等宣传海报。</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">四、联系方式</span></b><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">联系人：周经理</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;font-size:9pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">联系电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">0512</span>―<span lang=\"EN-US\">88989800</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">88989789<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">电子邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"mailto:799022456@qq.com\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: ; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt\" none?=\"\" roman?;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;color:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:=\"\" new=\"\" calibri?,?sans-serif?;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-