-US\">LED</span>电子显示屏，人数计数器、自助招聘摊位<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>个<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>常设招聘摊位<span lang=\"EN-US\">64</span>个，以及网络招聘室、视频招聘室、自助招聘摊位、面谈式招聘摊位等。实现了自助式求职招聘、摊位式洽谈招聘、网络招聘和视频招聘等功能。现将本次招聘会有关事项通知如下。</span><span style=\"font-family:''Tahoma'',''sans-serif'';color:black;font-size:9pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">一、主办、承办单位</span></b><span style=\"font-family:''Tahoma'',''sans-serif'';color:black;font-size:9pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">主办：吴江区人力资源和社会保障局</span><span style=\"font-family:''Tahoma'',''sans-serif'';color:black;font-size:9pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">承办：吴江区就管中心、吴江区人力资源市场</span><span style=\"font-family:''Tahoma'',''sans-serif'';color:black;font-size:9pt;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:13.5pt;margin:3.75pt 0cm;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:12pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">二、时间、地点</span></b><span style=\"font-family:''Tahoma'',''sans-serif'';color